Willcox Branch of Lieutenant Run, including Lee Park
City of Petersburg, Virginia

*Galax urceolata* (Poiret) Brummitt Coll. Date: 5/19/1998

Dense colony on lower N-facing slope at WPA bog inlet into
Willcox Lake; Lee Park. Possibly representing a natural 
occurrence at this site that was greatly augmented by the WPA
Wildflower Sanctuary project in the late 1930s.
